text: {| |} Aconit is a second-line multi-mission stealth frigate of the French Navy. Initially to be named , she is now the fourth French vessel named after the FNFL corvette . She took part in the Action of 9 April 2009. ==Gallery== Image:FS Aconit 1.jpg Image:FS Aconit 2.jpg Image:FS Aconit 3.jpg Image:FS Aconit 4.jpg Image:FS Aconit 5.jpg Image:FS Aconit 6.jpg Category:La Fayette- class frigates Category:Active frigates of France Category:1997 ships Category:Ships built in France
